{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01J996yYKkGZjLdy2KWp6h3S","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→ARAYES SHRAK - yes\n     2→Baked Eggs with Feta, Harissa Tomato Sauce & Coriander - no\n     3→CHLEBEK Z WARZYWAMI I BOCZKIEM - no\n     4→FINNISH MILK FLATBREADS + FINNISH POTATO FLATBREADS - yes\n     5→Faszerowana papryka - no\n     6→MIXED SEED CRISPBREAD - yes\n     7→OVERNIGHT STRAIGHT PIZZA DOUGH - yes\n     8→SAFFRON WHEAT BUNS WITH QUARK : COTTAGE CHEESE (VARIATION D) - no\n     9→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a59a0b2d-7c4a-45b6-b31c-a70904d94b94","uuid":"014bfef4-dbef-46ab-951b-9d1266d1ef61","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/7-9a83c46/results.txt","content":"ARAYES SHRAK - yes\nBaked Eggs with Feta, Harissa Tomato Sauce & Coriander - no\nCHLEBEK Z WARZYWAMI I BOCZKIEM - no\nFINNISH MILK FLATBREADS + FINNISH POTATO FLATBREADS - yes\nFaszerowana papryka - no\nMIXED SEED CRISPBREAD - yes\nOVERNIGHT STRAIGHT PIZZA DOUGH - yes\nSAFFRON WHEAT BUNS WITH QUARK : COTTAGE CHEESE (VARIATION D) - no\n","numLines":9,"startLine":1,"totalLines":9}}}
